> I haven't tried to trace this down yet, but I noticed a bug in recent
> multibyte-enabled zsh versions (including CVS):
>
>   % touch foo faa
>   % ls f{oo,a<TAB>       # pressing TAB results in:
>   % ls f{oo,aa,_         # (note: _ is the cursor) OK so far...
